Paper: hep-th/9607114

Date: 1996-07-15

Title: On the Minimal Model of Anyons

Authors: I.V. Gorbunov, S.M. Kuzenko and S.L. Lyakhovich

Comments: 17 pages, LaTex, no figures

Journal-ref: Int.J.Mod.Phys. A12 (1997) 4199-4215

We present new geometric formulations for the fractional spin particle modelson the minimal phase spaces. New consistent couplings of the anyon tobackground fields are constructed. The relationship between our approach andpreviously developed anyon models is discussed.